<c74object name='sp.descriptorcurves' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Descriptor scaling and curve application
</digest>
    <description>Descriptor scaling and curve application.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.descriptorcurves</o> object takes incoming descriptor data (descriptors only) and allows you to apply curves or common scalings to it. This is useful when moving from different unit types like dB, MIDI, amplitude, etc... or when you want to adjust the curve/sensitivity of a specific descriptor.
</discussion>

